      "content": "i get that it's better to check with a doctor but i don't really have the time right now and i'm already feeling so drained. i've seen some biohacking forums saying that \"loading doses\" like 50k iu is actually a standard way to jumpstart your system when you're deficient. if i only do it for like 14 days, wouldn't that be fine? it's just a short burst.",
